306
00:15:45,621 --> 00:15:48,155
"He taught them
to think happy thoughts

307
00:15:48,221 --> 00:15:51,088
and sprinkle them with
pixie dust so they could... "

308
00:15:51,155 --> 00:15:52,121
boys: Fly.

