455
00:24:19,607 --> 00:24:22,607
He don't know
the most important part.

456
00:24:26,041 --> 00:24:28,208
What's the most
important part?

457
00:24:29,707 --> 00:24:31,640
I knew the way, all right.

458
00:24:31,707 --> 00:24:32,841
