469
00:25:08,707 --> 00:25:10,007
Who knows why?

470
00:25:10,074 --> 00:25:12,407
New janitor, new rule.

471
00:25:12,474 --> 00:25:14,640
<i>Come on.
I never knew.</i>

472
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:18,707
I looked down at the guys.

473
00:25:18,774 --> 00:25:21,307
