474
00:25:22,707 --> 00:25:24,907
Don't sit down, you guys.
We got to find our way out.

475
00:25:24,974 --> 00:25:26,407
Come on.

476
00:25:31,974 --> 00:25:34,373
It was my fault.

477
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:36,741
